    <div class="active" id="showproduct">
      <h1 class='title' align="center">走进大师·姜一涵书画艺术展</h1>
      

<script src="/Templates/cn2014/js/ShopShow.js"></script>
      <div style="clear:both;"></div>
      <div class="editor" id="metbox">
        <div class="box" >
          <div><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 29px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"></span></span></strong>&nbsp;</p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><img title="1.姜一涵先生自画像.jpg" alt="1.姜一涵先生自画像.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161229/14830214599612425.jpg"/><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">姜一涵先生自画像</span></span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">姜一涵，字雪橘、逸中，山东昌邑人，台湾著名学者、书画家。</span></span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">此次展览</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">是潍坊市</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">第二十二届鲁台经贸洽谈会期间</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">举行的重要活动，</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">先生</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">展出了自己</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">不同时期创作的50件艺术精品，旨在为家乡的文博事业贡献自己的一份力量。</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><img title="2.涧.jpg" alt="2.涧.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161229/14830214723950483.jpg"/><img title="3.排队的金鱼.jpg" alt="3.排队的金鱼.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161229/14830214807763838.jpg"/><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 184px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">涧 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;排队的金鱼</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><img title="4.散僧·游侠.jpg" alt="4.散僧·游侠.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161229/14830214901409208.jpg"/><img title="5.不忧·常醒.jpg" alt="5.不忧·常醒.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161229/14830214984635343.jpg"/><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 128px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">散僧·游侠 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;不忧·常醒</span></span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">姜一涵先生在书画艺术、书画研究、书画教育领域成就显著，德艺双馨，享有崇高社会声誉。几十年来，在复杂和变迁的环境中，他始终对艺术抱以至高的理想和真挚的热爱，以一个真正的艺术家的无畏胆略和率真性情，在丹青事业上做不懈的追求与探索。姜一涵先生在亲历中西文化相互碰撞激荡的人生旅程中，坚持以中国文化为根本，吸收融化西方艺术，形成了中西绘画意蕴贯通融合，并且富有哲学性和文化内涵的独特成果和崭新经验。他的书画作品在美国和亚洲受到了很高的赞誉，被誉为“东方的毕加索</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">，其绘画和书法作品在国际美术界享有极高的赞誉。让我们满怀敬意，共同走进姜一涵先生</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">“</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">出新意于法度之中，寄妙理于豪放之外</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">的艺术世界，同时也希望先生高尚的奉献精神和精湛的艺术创作将永远并茂相映，光华灿烂！</span></span></p><p></p><script src="/inc/AspCms_VisitsAdd.asp?id=179"></script>
            <div id="metinfo_additional"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
